Monthly Training Overview

During January 2026, I participated in intensive cloud engineering and Linux systems training focused on AWS infrastructure, storage services, networking fundamentals, and system administration best practices. The training combined instructor-led lectures, live demonstrations, troubleshooting scenarios, and hands-on implementation to reinforce real-world cloud operations skills.

Instruction emphasized building, securing, troubleshooting, and maintaining scalable cloud environments using AWS services and Linux operating systems.

