Progress & Learning Outcomes

Throughout January 2026, I significantly strengthened my technical foundation in cloud infrastructure and Linux operations. Hands-on practice reinforced how compute, storage, and networking components integrate within AWS environments to support secure and scalable applications. The training improved my confidence in troubleshooting real-world cloud issues, managing Linux systems, and designing production-ready architectures aligned with industry best practices.

